                                <p>冊</p>
                                <decoNote>畫冊為十六開十二幅。經摺裝。題簽空白，封皮為硬面包有紅色絲織物帶藍色綠色瑞獸祥雲幾何花紋。
                                          封皮封底的絲織物表面有磨損抽絲。本幅為絹本設色工筆畫，對幅為空白紙本。畫心裝裱在白色絲織物上，
                                          邊為白色，已汎黃。
                                          This album contains twelve paintings, meticulously rendered on silk using traditional
                                          brushwork techniques. It is a concertina-style binding, featuring a cover crafted from 
                                          red silk embellished with intricate patterns in blue and green, portraying auspicious 
                                          mythical creatures and celestial clouds. However, the silk covering the front and back 
                                          displays signs of wear and slight fraying.
                                          The paintings themselves are mounted on a white silk background, with the edges having 
                                          acquired a yellowish hue over time. The title label on this album's cover is left blank.
                                </decoNote>
                            </binding>
